# Runtime & Env
- Requires `.env` with `UPBIT_ACCESS_KEY`, `UPBIT_SECRET_KEY`. If absent, system auto-falls back to paper mode.
- Flask secret key must be set via `FLASK_SECRET_KEY` in `.env` (see [web/app.py](mdc:web/app.py)).
- Default host/port via env: `FLASK_HOST`, `FLASK_PORT`.
- Initialize DB via `python main.py --init-db`.
